snippet.title: Super Mario Bob-omb Blast - 2023 Trailer - NFGD Cut
snippet.description:
An edited version of the 2023 trailer for the Nintendo Fan-Games Direct.
Merry Christmas and Happy New(er) Year everyone!

~Original Description~

Super Mario Bob-omb Blast is a full scale New Super Mario Bros. Wii mod that aims to improve upon the original game's mechanics while adding bombs to the mix!

This mod will feature completely the entire game, from the levels, to the menus or the graphics. It aims to be a completely new experience unlike any other mod.

You can join our discord server if you want to be notified immediately when a new sneak peek is released: https://discord.gg/XWAxgK86hB

Or follow our twitter account: https://twitter.com/BombCrew266226
